-- ==============================================================
-- item-finder-by-iskrumpie.lua
-- Submitted by @iSkrumpie  (https://github.com/ramisotti13-eng/farever-minimap/pull/52)
-- Tested against farever-mod v0.6.3
-- License: MIT
--
-- Search every item, material and mob in the game by name.
-- Click a result to see where it drops, which mobs carry it,
-- how to craft it, and -- for ore / plant nodes -- navigate to
-- the nearest one on the map with a live compass arrow.
--
-- Data source: FareverDB (fareverdb.com) -- auto-scraped at build
-- time and embedded as static tables (require/dofile unavailable
-- in the plugin sandbox).  Re-run scrape_fareverdb.py after a
-- game patch, then build_item_finder.py to refresh.
--
-- v1.0.0 (2026-05-25):
--   + Item search  -- prefix-first, then contains, up to 25 results
--   + Mob search   -- same index, type-filtered via tab buttons
--   + Item detail  -- rarity / type / sell price
--   + NODE LOCATIONS -- POI count + nav arrow to nearest ore/plant node
--   + DROP TABLE   -- full FareverDB loot-table percentages, colour-coded
--   + DROPPED BY   -- list of mobs with %, level, zone (up to 10 shown)
--   + CRAFTED VIA  -- recipe ingredients + crafting job + level
--   + Mob detail   -- level, type, zone; drop list; [->] jumps to item
--   + hero_locked event clears nav on zone transitions
--   + Search query + filter tab persisted via farever.store
-- ==============================================================

